      <title>匈牙利福林跌至两年低点，通货膨胀加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/hungarian-inflation-quickens-amid-forint-plunge-to-two-year-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利的通货膨胀连续第二个月加速，因为食品和服务成本的上涨以及福林的暴跌使价格增长更接近央行容忍度的上限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/hungarian-inflation-quickens-amid-forint-plunge-to-two-year-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
